{"tid":222350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"UCLA都走去考差佬。香港學生點夠爭？","createTime":"2017-04-29T12:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T06:12:57.000Z","uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba1470039fdf657d56f044546cb3f6d1090a39e1","tid":222350,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"今年24歲、在UCLA畢業的高先生投考督察，他指，城大已收取他入讀法律博士課程，惟當警員是他由細到大的夢想，因此希望可成功應聘，「如果收我唔會揀讀JD。」高先生指對商業罪案調查科最有興趣，對於7警被判罪，他坦言，有些較偏激的朋友因過去的佔中事年反對他應徵督察，「但警察始終係我想做嘅工」，至於近年有不少休班警犯罪，他強調，「我絕對唔會係呢啲休班警囉。」"},{"pid":"3e0efda1024352956ec371d4d1b846cc8b56499f","tid":222350,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170429/large/1493443304_47e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170429%2Flarge%2F1493443304_47e1.jpg&h=1738b0d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖左為UCLA"},{"pid":"839c85996aed0ddbfc903446d31643f633cf5381","tid":222350,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:57:19.000Z","msg":"咁嘅樣係UCLA生唔生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3632f2dc89b70db32b9f92af71b973662421a821","tid":222350,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63533ae6e0c1723a6c52c7c31e1b3621e3d89b59","tid":222350,"uid":46323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"真係蝗樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa840386391a1e1b20faa80b052a4937fc98b6f","tid":222350,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解大陸仔嘴角成日都有墨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北佬既gene?"},{"pid":"33956061d5ab792d3ab9e3f044b